 "html": "<p>Mens is nooit te oud om te leer nie.  So gesels ek en my koskind, Herman Lensing en hy vertel vir my van die sjokoladeblokkies met 3 bestandele.  Ek het dit gemaak en dit is &#8216;n wenner en heerlik. &#8216;n Vinnige nagereg wat ek glo lekker saam met vla kan smaak of sommer net n bederf vir wanneer die soetlus jou beetpak.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-031.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1264\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 031\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-031-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>BESTANDELE:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>250 ml Nutella</li>\n<li>100 ml koekmeel</li>\n<li>2 eiers<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1253\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>gooi alles in n mengbak.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-004.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1254\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 004\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-004-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>klits met n handklitser tot net gemeng<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-006.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1255\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 006\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-006-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>spuit n oondbakkie met Spray en Cook en gooi die mengsel in die bak<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1256\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-011-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>bak vir 20 minute by 180°C<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-017.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1257\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 017\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-017-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>laat dit afkoel en geniet die heerlikheid</li>\n<li>ek het die orige Nutella wat in die bottel was bo-oor gesmeer<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-0271.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1263\" alt=\"Nutella blokkies blog 027\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Nutella-blokkies-blog-0271-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
